Maxima did nothing, just watched the fembot leave. 

She glared at Hevn for a moment. 'Similar tastes? Please!' she thought to 
herself. If he wished to be like Hydras, so be it. She wanted to be there 
when Hydras found out that there was a look alike. 

The other part, the flirting, was not something she took well too. It was a 
Decepticon conditioning. She would keep her optics on this one, that was for 
sure.

Turning her attention back to the CR that Hydras was in. She waited. Despite 
the damage she received from the little spar between her & Blackstorm.. she 
would not repair in one of the CRs yet. 

--part1_18a.19505a61.2be214b1_boundary
